platforms.name: mastodon
platforms.description: Mastodon is a free, open-source social network server based on the open web protocol ActivityPub. The social focus of the project is a viable decentralized alternative to commercial social media silos that returns the control of the content distribution channels to the people. The technical focus of the project is a good user interface, a clean REST API for 3rd party apps and robust anti-abuse tools.
platforms.tagline: Your self-hosted, globally interconnected microblogging community
